{"skipTransitionList":[],"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3035_00_01","textHome":"我是街上的便当店“千秋屋”家的看板娘，@千秋理子！喜欢的事是算术和打饭！@爸爸妈妈还有老师都经常夸我是个乖孩子！@店里的推荐菜是炸鸡块和健康沙拉便当！@务必要来试吃一下哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3035_00_18","textHome":"晚上便当屋需要收拾，陪我在家的人是爸爸！@虽然有些害羞……@现在我们偶尔还会一起（悄悄话）……@这是秘密啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3035_00_19","textHome":"我的彩色叉签能把问题全都解决得更漂亮了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":303500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":303500}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3035_00_20","textHome":"转一个圈～啪！看，我是不是变了些呢!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303500,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"